.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-STATE-PENDING-COUNT" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-state-pending-count \- FEAT-2185 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-state-pending-count
.SH DESCRIPTION
verb for lightning CLI (FEAT-2185).
.PP
Counts channels that are not yet in CHANNELD_NORMAL state (i.e., pending open, closing, or otherwise transitioning).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
